------------------------------------------------------
Conclusion
------------------------------------------------------

This script adds an important layer to the project by
moving from general statistics to detailed matchup
analysis.

It shows not only how teams perform overall, but also
how they perform against specific opponents, providing
a more complete and realistic view of the data.